        "data": {
          "id": "comment_lf_430_001",
          "body": "## Investigation Results (09:00 UTC)\n\n### Benchmark Baseline\n- Current build time: **480 seconds (8m)**\n- Cache hit rate: **~35%** (cold start 100% miss)\n- Bottleneck: Turborepo task graph re-computation\n\n### Profiling Data\n- `core/lightfast` build: 2m45s (includes unnecessary bundling)\n- `apps/console` build: 3m20s (Next.js page compilation)\n- Package graph: 47 packages with serial dependencies\n\n### Root Causes\n1. **Turborepo cache mismatch**: Pipeline hashing not capturing all inputs\n2. **Next.js config**: Compiling all pages eagerly, no incremental builds\n3. **Package graph**: Sequential ordering when parallelizable\n\n### Optimization Plan\n1. **Turborepo**: Fix cache key generation, enable persistent cache layer\n2. **Next.js**: Enable incremental static regeneration, optimize webpack config\n3. **Graph**: Restructure dependencies for parallel task execution\n\nEstimated impact: **50-80% improvement** (480s → 120s)\n\nStarting implementation now.",
          "createdAt": "2026-02-09T09:00:00Z",
